{"id":"int-db2b047e","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-18T17:57:50.080993Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-t0o","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Phase 3 BeadsService done: typed read API (listIssues/readyIssues/showIssue), mutations (createIssue/claimIssue/updateIssue/closeIssue/reopenIssue), BeadsError taxonomy, CreateIssueInput/UpdateIssueInput, StubCommandRunner, 15 new tests. swift test: 32/32 green."}}
{"id":"int-f4216879","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-18T18:05:01.592138Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-ogw","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Phase 4 done: @Observable @MainActor IssueStore with reload (parallel list+ready), select/clear, mutations (create/claim/update/close/reopen + claimSelected/closeSelected) auto-reload on success, errorMessage on failure. Kanban-mapped computed columns (backlog/ready/inProgress/blocked/done) per PRD §5.1. Sort by priority asc then updatedAt desc. 10 new tests. swift test: 42/42 green."}}
{"id":"int-5664ba9e","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-18T18:15:34.871062Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-dwz","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Phase 5 done: KanbanColumn enum + KanbanStateMapper pure function in BeadsContract. Rules: closed→done, in_progress→inProgress, blocked→blocked, in readyIDs→ready, else→backlog. Unknown status falls back to backlog with isKnownStatus flag. IssueStore refactored to use mapper + exposes unknownStatusIssueIDs/hasUnknownStatus. 11 new tests (10 mapper + 1 store). swift test: 53/53 green."}}
