{"id":"int-ca4afbcc","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-19T03:30:41.498557Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-5hz","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Fixed B1 (reloadTask identity check), B2 (status=ready maps to .ready), H1 (AgentProfileStore dedup against built-in IDs and within custom list, addProfile rejects built-in overwrite & dedups by id), H2 (BeadsService validates id on show/claim/update/close/reopen). 79 tests green (+7 regression tests)."}}
