{"id":"int-512c8b50","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-19T08:35:45.608852Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-51a","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Agent workflow generalization selesai (scope di luar PRD): tambah built-in Codex Code Executor + 4 capability fields (commandArgsTemplate, canExecuteCode, shouldClaimIssue, shouldCloseIssue) backward-compat via custom Codable init. Tambah Copy Command action + button gating per capability. 104 SPM test hijau. Catatan: nomor 'Phase 10' di title misleading — bertabrakan dengan PRD §10 Phase 10 (Testing Strategy)."}}
{"id":"int-df6b4321","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-19T08:45:46.455053Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-oy2","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Added decoder resilience tests for unknown fields and wrapped payloads, preserved raw JSON on BeadsError.jsonDecodeFailed via IssueStore state, and exposed the latest decode failure in the debug panel alongside command history."}}
{"id":"int-9888e2c5","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-19T08:53:04.650184Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-b9v","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Done column window 24h: BeadIssue tambah closedAt, BeadsService.closedIssues calls 'bd list --status=closed --json', IssueStore fetch+filter pakai injected now() + doneVisibilityWindow (default 24h from AppPreferences), fail-soft kalau bd lama tidak support flag. 5 new tests: service call shape, fresh-closed populates Done, stale filtered out, zero window skips fetch, fetch failure silent. swift test 112 hijau, app build SUCCEEDED."}}
{"id":"int-add5d52f","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-19T09:06:58.236462Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-u6x","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Expanded BeadsAppError to the PRD 8.1 taxonomy with user-facing messages and recovery suggestions, mapped bd/service/validator failures into the new cases, and added tests for every case plus the new error translations."}}
{"id":"int-87e1b390","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-19T09:12:40.715653Z","actor":"Rayne-lope","issue_id":"Workstation-mt8","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Added actionable setup hints in the welcome validation UI for missing .beads, missing AGENTS.md, and missing bd CLI, with per-hint copy-to-clipboard commands and model tests for hint selection."}}
